{"tid":1308841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(同一陣線) 民陣出聲明屌柒肥佬藍線暴徒行為！(各有各做)","createTime":"2019-07-12T03:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T04:01:41.000Z","uid":9566,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d2b686c36f77effcab4115fcb0464e33e7f83987","tid":1308841,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:53:41.000Z","msg":"民陣譴責暴徒襲擊、破壞連儂牆及自發市民<br />\n<br />\n民陣非常關注近日各區有市民因為保護連儂牆被建制派支持者、休班警員滋擾、破壞，更有市民被<span style=\"color: red;\">暴徒</span>襲擊、受傷，昨夜大埔有守護連儂牆的市民被襲擊至手臂骨折，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民陣對暴徒的種種行為表示極度憤怒，予以最強烈譴責</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆的諸位戰友連日來盡心盡力，為陰沉的城市添上色彩，以memo紙為市民打氣，為年輕人增添正面氣氛，預防一切我們不欲見到的悲劇再次發生，實在是「做埋政府嗰份」，但卻多番被建制派支持者、休班警員滋擾、破壞，敢問各位居心何在。<br />\n<br />\n民陣嚴正提醒林鄭月娥，不要再用政治言辭處理民眾訴求，認真回應五大訴求，堂堂正正撤回條例，管好下屬，否則莫談和解。<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線<br />\n2019年7月12日<br />\n<br />\n小編按︰<br />\n#唔係話你地搞暴動<br />\n#係話你地少數人展現出暴徒嘅行為<br />\n#睇唔明返去問盧偉聰囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5E6LB4b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5E6LB4b.png&h=fbee4dee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.517931904920872/2351620314885346/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2Fphotos%2Fa.517931904920872%2F2351620314885346%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0FLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=46bc80f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.517931904920872/2351620314885346/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"d5bf4b36388ed6df55e1de4f5ed6650e048251d6","tid":1308841,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}